          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Robert E. Lee Statue Removal Act</b></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of the Interior to develop a plan to remove the monument to Robert E. Lee at Antietam National Battlefield in Maryland. </p> <p>Interior must submit to Congress a time line for the removal of such monument in accordance with the plan. </p>]]></text>
